---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import pengaturanHalaman from '../../content/pengaturanHalaman/data.json';
import pengaturanUtama from '../../content/pengaturanUtama/data.json';
---

<Layout title="Program SMP - MTQ Tarbiyah Sunnah">
<main>
<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="relative w-full h-[60vh] min-h-[400px] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
<img alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center" src={pengaturanHalaman.heroSmp || "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida/AP1WRLszwn5N-x9727cd7uNdMM0yrkccUouVYTKKXHz4avJ4m5djA1Avzj1uq8dK8cAPW5tOqSH1PevKcHlNgq56QuogIJm07ABO_8nP1LrmmtpR-E10w8X4KJWMnDVX27yrC_TmJqNH6tWSaIRBJiN7ow32uwgftGY6Tdw050Vp1w9ML0Cg2T1Z_y3pUBgJrD3BagRhLVFhKZ9-n9hYHmsTo8m0_qS12zapqP3D6giZtXSOySmabe31m4TLtKs"}/>
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-surface via-surface/80 to-transparent"></div>
</div>
<div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop text-center mt-xl">
<div class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 bg-surface-container-low/80 backdrop-blur-sm px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-6 border border-primary-fixed/30">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-sm">school</span>
<span class="text-label-sm text-primary uppercase tracking-widest">Program Pendidikan Menengah</span>
</div>
<h1 class="text-display-lg md:text-[56px] leading-tight text-primary mb-6 drop-shadow-sm">
    SMP Tahfizh
</h1>
<p class="text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    Membangun generasi Qur'ani dengan pemahaman salafus shalih, memadukan tahfizh Al-Qur'an intensif, dirosah islamiyah, dan pendidikan akademik formal yang berkualitas.
</p>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Kurikulum Bento Grid -->
<section class="py-xl bg-surface-container-lowest border-y border-[#E9EEE7]">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
<div class="text-center mb-12">
<h2 class="text-headline-lg text-primary mb-4">Struktur Kurikulum</h2>
<p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    Kurikulum yang dirancang komprehensif untuk menyeimbangkan ilmu syar'i dan ilmu duniawi sebagai bekal santri.
</p>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
<!-- Tahfizh Card -->
<div class="bg-surface border border-[#E9EEE7] rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-[0_4px_20px_rgba(47,80,33,0.08)] transition-all duration-300 group">
<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary-container text-on-primary-container flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">menu_book</span>
</div>
<h3 class="text-headline-md text-primary mb-3">Tahfizh Al-Qur'an</h3>
<p class="text-[14px] font-sans text-on-surface-variant">
    Target hafalan mutqin minimal 20 Juz selama masa pendidikan dengan metode ziyadah dan muraja'ah yang terstruktur.
</p>
</div>
<!-- Diniyah Card -->
<div class="bg-surface border border-[#E9EEE7] rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-[0_4px_20px_rgba(47,80,33,0.08)] transition-all duration-300 group">
<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-tertiary-container text-on-tertiary-container flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">mosque</span>
</div>
<h3 class="text-headline-md text-primary mb-3">Dirosah Islamiyah</h3>
<p class="text-[14px] font-sans text-on-surface-variant">
    Mempelajari Aqidah, Fiqih, Sirah, dan Adab berlandaskan pemahaman manhaj salafus shalih.
</p>
</div>
<!-- Bahasa Arab Card -->
<div class="bg-surface border border-[#E9EEE7] rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-[0_4px_20px_rgba(47,80,33,0.08)] transition-all duration-300 group">
<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-secondary-container text-on-secondary-container flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">translate</span>
</div>
<h3 class="text-headline-md text-primary mb-3">Bahasa Arab</h3>
<p class="text-[14px] font-sans text-on-surface-variant">
    Pembelajaran intensif Nahwu, Shorof, dan Muhadatsah untuk memahami literatur Islam klasik.
</p>
</div>
<!-- Akademik Card -->
<div class="bg-surface border border-[#E9EEE7] rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-[0_4px_20px_rgba(47,80,33,0.08)] transition-all duration-300 group">
<div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-surface-variant text-on-surface-variant flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">science</span>
</div>
<h3 class="text-headline-md text-primary mb-3">Pendidikan Akademik</h3>
<p class="text-[14px] font-sans text-on-surface-variant">
    Kurikulum Diknas yang disesuaikan (Matematika, IPA, Bahasa Indonesia, dll) untuk bekal melanjutkan ke jenjang berikutnya.
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Profil Lulusan / Keunggulan -->
<section class="py-xl bg-surface relative overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-pattern opacity-50"></div>
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop relative z-10">
<div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12">
<div class="lg:w-1/2">
<div class="aspect-square md:aspect-video lg:aspect-square rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg border border-[#E9EEE7]">
<img alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida/AP1WRLsoN003K1-XgkIFAadcGIc_x4OqQfglK73QyUuWzQ_AoU-6NV4cND5wlnjA9OtY_zKW9HCHY93k3h6A6D9O4Rj15ZeqsnKHDkw-CzF5AdcnOSVqUU8oG5Y7Mh-6QrnwtY3qh2IVvqG35FcqE5XTVanWB38GpdjL4rpoHpvcE95vNomQ5OAdDxQ6BXAG5jaH-Oyw9tp6kSiMx_PPpZABrGccXgPojdireoBNSfu5FMn5Ia84WxPek7emIRg"/>
</div>
</div>
<div class="lg:w-1/2 space-y-8">
<div>
<h2 class="text-headline-lg text-primary mb-4">Profil Lulusan</h2>
<p class="text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">
    Kami berkomitmen mencetak generasi yang tidak hanya unggul dalam hafalan, namun juga berakhlak mulia dan siap menghadapi tantangan masa depan.
</p>
</div>
<div class="space-y-4">
<div class="flex gap-4">
<div class="mt-1">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">check_circle</span>
</div>
<div>
<h4 class="text-label-md text-primary">Target Hafal 20 Juz Al-Qur'an</h4>
<p class="text-[14px] font-sans text-on-surface-variant">Dengan bacaan yang tartil dan mutqin sesuai kaidah tajwid.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-4">
<div class="mt-1">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">check_circle</span>
</div>
<div>
<h4 class="text-label-md text-primary">Beraqidah Shahihah</h4>
<p class="text-[14px] font-sans text-on-surface-variant">Memiliki aqidah yang lurus sesuai pemahaman salaful ummah.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-4">
<div class="mt-1">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">check_circle</span>
</div>
<div>
<h4 class="text-label-md text-primary">Mampu Berbahasa Arab Dasar</h4>
<p class="text-[14px] font-sans text-on-surface-variant">Menguasai kaidah dasar bahasa Arab untuk memahami literatur syar'i.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex gap-4">
<div class="mt-1">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary">check_circle</span>
</div>
<div>
<h4 class="text-label-md text-primary">Ijazah Formal SMP</h4>
<p class="text-[14px] font-sans text-on-surface-variant">Mendapatkan ijazah kelulusan SMP yang diakui negara.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- CTA Section -->
<section class="py-xl bg-surface-container-high border-t border-[#E9EEE7]">
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop text-center">
<h2 class="text-headline-lg text-primary mb-6">Bergabunglah Bersama Kami</h2>
<p class="text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-8">
    Pendaftaran Santri Baru (SPMB) SMP Tahfizh MTQ Tarbiyah Sunnah Tahun Ajaran Baru telah dibuka. Kuota terbatas.
</p>
<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
<a href="/spmb" class="bg-secondary text-on-secondary text-label-md px-8 py-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:shadow-[0_4px_20px_rgba(149,74,0,0.2)] transition-all duration-300">
    Daftar Sekarang
</a>
<a href={pengaturanUtama.linkBrosur || "#"} target={pengaturanUtama.linkBrosur ? "_blank" : undefined} rel={pengaturanUtama.linkBrosur ? "noopener noreferrer" : undefined} class="btn-secondary !bg-transparent !border-primary !text-primary hover:!bg-primary-fixed/20 transition-all duration-300">
    Unduh Brosur
</a>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</main>
</Layout>
